reviewText: GREAT PRESENTATION! Does anyone KNOW WHERE I COULD PURCHASE 'THE MAGIC ROUNDABOUT "DVD in the Region 1 Format ASAP ? Thank You Kindly !

Absolutely love this cartoon. The only place i was able to watch it was on Cinemoi on DirecTV, but when it was dropped i was left out in the cold. Even though I can only watch this region 2 on my computer it is well worth it. It is a delightful cartoon. I wish more were available.
